Hey I would use the Search API for this
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/crm/search>

Any internal property names in the 'properties' array will be returned to you

`<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts/search>`
```{
  "properties": [
    "phone",
    "mobilephone",
    "hs_whatsapp_phone_number"
  ],
  "filterGroups": [
    {
      "filters": [
        {
          "propertyName": "associations.deal",
          "operator": "EQ",
          "value": "&lt;deal_id&gt;"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}```
Example Response of Contacts found on my Deal within my test portal:
